import axios from"axios";const API_BASE_URL="/api";// ✅ Use relative path since frontend and backend are on the same origin
export const getNearestOffices=async(latitude,longitude)=>{try{const response=await axios.get("".concat(API_BASE_URL,"/offices?lat=").concat(latitude,"&lng=").concat(longitude));return response.data;}catch(error){console.error("Error fetching nearest offices:",error);return[];}};
